I hate to think that inside me is growing...

55
00:07:18,657 --> 00:07:22,170
It's a baby, Gerry, that's all it is.

56
00:07:34,669 --> 00:07:36,830
Louis you stay away from that..

57
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:39,237
John get out of the mud!

58
00:07:40,224 --> 00:07:42,545
The black is a nigger now
You smell like one too, I bet!

59
00:07:44,189 --> 00:07:46,739
...

60
